				<h2>What can I do if a useless answer is about to receive a bounty?</h2>
<p>I have a question with a bounty and a <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/a/40440/4395">leading answer that's useless</a> and appears not even to have understood the question. Is there anything I can do to prevent the bad answer from receiving the bounty?</p>

